direct way of formatting numbers with group separators:

    >>> import locale
    >>> locale.setlocale(locale.LC_ALL, 'English_United States.1252')
    'English_United States.1252'
    >>> conv = locale.localeconv()          # get a mapping of conventions
    >>> x = 1234567.8
